<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
- Sort all vertices order by X, Y
- Find widest angle vertex from base vertices.
# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
- sort array (nlogn)
- insert all vertices which x == 0 and x == max(X)
- i = 0
- run below while loop for biggest Y vertex, smallest Y vertex
- while i<n-1 
    for j=i+1~n : 
        find wide angle vertice
        set i to j
- return vertices from set
